+------------------------------------------------------+
|     |   +----------------+                     |     |
|     |                                          |     |
|     |   +------------+                         |     |
|     |                                          |     +--> 1 Page
|     |   +-----------------+                    |     |
|     |                                          |     |  /projects/list?limit=4
|     |   +---------+                            |     |
+------------------------------------------------------+
